Lastly, the value of the option is solved below: 

&nbsp;

$$\begin{aligned}
\textbf{C}&=\frac{\text{Expected payoff}}{\text{e}^{\text{rt}}}\\[20pt]
&=\frac{\$5.62}{2.71828^{(0.05)(0.50)}}\\[20pt]
&=\frac{\$5.62}{2.71828^{(0.025)}}\\[20pt]
&=\frac{\$5.62}{1.0253}\\[20pt]
&=\boxed{\$5.48}
\end{aligned}$$


Thus, the value of the call option is $5.48.
